### Chords API
### Base URL: /api/v1/data/chords/

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1/data

### Get all chords
GET {{baseUrl}}/chords/ HTTP/1.1

### Get chord by ID
# Replace with actual ID from the list response
@chordId = 1

GET {{baseUrl}}/chords/{{chordId}}/ HTTP/1.1

### Get non-existent chord (expects 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chords/99999/ HTTP/1.1
